CL-DevIL is a set of [[Common Lisp]] [[CFFI]] bindings to the [http://openil.sourceforge.net/ DevIL] image loading and manipulation library, previously known as OpenIL. DevIL provides speedy loading and saving features for a wide range of image formats, as well as support for various OpenGL and DirectX features.

